history.content:
Hi, I recently got an email that they expanded CS 161 to have additional discussion sections. I am currently #50 on the waitlist. However, the new discussion sections conflict with my CS 170 lecture sections. I can't figure out a way to swap discussion sections for CS 161 without dropping the class. But, if I do drop the class, I'll go to the end of the waitlist but be able to have the new discussion sections, with the aforementioned conflict (?). What should I do?

Thanks!
